* Install required Perl modules if necessary:
  
  - Encode
  - English
  - Getopt::Long
  - JSON
  - Net::LDAPS
  - Net::LDAP::Util
  
  Adapt use lib setting at the beginning of adMgr.pl if necessary.

* Move adMgr.pl somewhere in your $PATH

* Edit adMgrrc.dist according to your local setup and move to
  $HOME/.adMgrrc
